message.body: How goes it? Where are you based? I'm in north FL, where hurricane season is off to a running start!
Oh no! Be safe! I'm in Philly
Right on. What do you do in Philly? I used to live in west Philly some years ago.
Oh cool. I'm an O&M instructor and a standardized patient and a puppeteer. I used to live in west. Why'd ya move to fl?
I know what a puppeteer is. The other stuff tho, huh? I'm from FL, came back to be near family again. Didnt really enjoy philly at the time tho, no offense.
I do electrical work for money. For joy i do pretty much anything involving water, especially diving & paddlin. I like travel & i'm also pretty civicly engaged.
Cool yea I'm not a jig Philly fan either, hopefully moving in a year or two. O&M = I work with people who are blind and teach travel skills
Stand. Patient (sp) = I pretend to be sick and grade drs for a national standardized test on how good they dr me.
Right on. Where do you want to move to?
